&lt;p class=MsoNormal style='text-align:justify'>&lt;span style='font-size:12.0pt'>            Science
deals with the experience of recurrent natural processes in the present. The
technology science uses enhances the degree and kinds of sense perception in
the natural realm.&lt;/span>&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>KNOWING BY FAITH</title><link>https://christir.org/essays/evidences/know-how-we-epistemology/knowing-by-faith-2/</link><pubDate>Thu, 02 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://christir.org/essays/evidences/know-how-we-epistemology/knowing-by-faith-2/</guid><description>&lt;style>
